name: Lushtemples — Spirit Animal
description:
I like that you bind Earth with the sky.
That you feed on History.
I love to confront your complexity, even though you look so simple.
I appreciate your stability, how you bend but don't break.
You're getting older, yet born anew every year.
I like all the stories of those scars you wear.
I like how some respect you, and when they don’t, you ignore them.
How your head is called a crown.
Yet no one worships you _ one doesn’t worship the temple. ​
I love that you play with the kids ; won’t forget how much you played
with me ! How you taught me to calm down, to sit back, to listen ;
I like how you offer the littles a shelter, and allow them to watch
the world from upstairs.
